<topic template="Default" xmlns:xsi="http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema-instance" xsi:noNamespaceSchemaLocation="../helpproject.xsd">
  <title translate="true">Control Structures</title>
  <body>
    <header>
      <para styleclass="Heading1"><text styleclass="Heading1" translate="true">Control Structures</text></para>
    </header>
    <para styleclass="Normal"><text styleclass="Normal" translate="true">Smalltalk has no control structures like if built into the language. Instead, Smalltalk uses messages sent to the true or false objects.</text></para>
    <para styleclass="Normal"><table rowcount="2" colcount="2" style="cell-padding:0px; cell-spacing:0px; border-width:0px; border-spacing:0px; border-collapse:collapse; cell-border-width:1px; border-color:#000000; border-style:solid;">
      <tr style="vertical-align:top">
        <td style="vertical-align:middle; width:312px;">
          <para style="margin-top:7px; margin-bottom:7px;"><text style="font-family:&apos;Times New Roman&apos;; font-size:12pt; font-weight:bold; color:#000000;" translate="true">Java</text></para>
        </td>
        <td style="vertical-align:middle; width:312px;">
          <para style="margin-top:7px; margin-bottom:7px;"><text style="font-family:&apos;Times New Roman&apos;; font-size:12pt; font-weight:bold; color:#000000;" translate="true">Smalltalk</text></para>
        </td>
      </tr>
      <tr style="vertical-align:top">
        <td style="vertical-align:middle; width:312px;">
          <para style="margin-top:7px; margin-bottom:7px;"><text style="font-family:&apos;Times New Roman&apos;; font-size:9pt; color:#000000;" translate="true">if (tries &gt; 5)</text><br/><text style="font-family:&apos;Times New Roman&apos;; font-size:9pt; color:#000000;" translate="true">return &quot;Too many tries&quot;;</text><br/><text style="font-family:&apos;Times New Roman&apos;; font-size:9pt; color:#000000;" translate="true">else</text><br/><text style="font-family:&apos;Times New Roman&apos;; font-size:9pt; color:#000000;" translate="true">return &quot;Trying again&quot;;</text></para>
        </td>
        <td style="vertical-align:middle; width:312px;">
          <para style="margin-top:7px; margin-bottom:7px;"><text style="font-family:&apos;Times New Roman&apos;; font-size:9pt; color:#000000;" translate="true">tries &gt; 5</text><br/><text style="font-family:&apos;Times New Roman&apos;; font-size:9pt; color:#000000;" translate="true">ifTrue: [^&apos;Too many tries&apos;]</text><br/><text style="font-family:&apos;Times New Roman&apos;; font-size:9pt; color:#000000;" translate="true">ifFalse: [^&apos;Trying again&apos;]</text></para>
        </td>
      </tr>
    </table></para>
    <para styleclass="Normal"><text styleclass="Normal" translate="true">Notice that the ^ returns from the method, not just the block.</text></para>
  </body>
